in my life.

39:05.177 --> 39:08.378
Tell you what,
that right there's gonna
be some high-dollar liquor.

39:10.082 --> 39:11.414
Check that out.

39:11.416 --> 39:13.149
Running good, man.

39:15.587 --> 39:17.854
That's a good stream
