next set of stills.

39:39.745 --> 39:42.112
Honey, cherry, wheat.

39:42.114 --> 39:44.914
You didn't think
it would be that strong,
did you?

39:44.916 --> 39:46.349
It's about a 105.

39:47.386 --> 39:48.585
There you go.

39:48.587 --> 39:50.687
Yeah, kenny,
you're probably right,
probably 105.

39:50.689 --> 39:53.857
-[all laughing]
-[tickle] hold on there,
brother.

39:53.859 --> 39:56.326
<i>  We finished running</i>
<i>  our small pots</i>

39:56.328 --> 39:58.862
<i>  and our big pots</i>
