To most moonshiners that would
be one hell of a day
under their belt.

40:06.138 --> 40:08.304
But our day's only
halfway through.

40:10.208 --> 40:13.243
It probably ain't going to be
too much longer
that's gonna be running.

40:13.912 --> 40:15.211
There she come, boys.

40:15.814 --> 40:16.880
[kenny] tell you what, fellas,

40:17.149 --> 40:20.150
this one's pouring it out,
I can tell you that much.

40:20.385 --> 40:21.384
[tickle] hell, yeah.

