I believe this part is
your old drawers.

42:03.421 --> 42:05.021
Oh, they're way too white.

42:05.023 --> 42:07.824
I don't know why we didn't
think about bringing
a little pump.

42:07.826 --> 42:08.992
Damn, it smells good,
