<i>  but it's all flavor</i>
<i>  at this point, so,</i>

42:28.013 --> 42:29.279
we feel good about it.

42:29.848 --> 42:30.980
Look at it.

42:30.982 --> 42:33.383
Kinda reminds me
of castrating cattle.

42:33.385 --> 42:35.385
I never did castrate no cows.

42:35.854 --> 42:37.687
With the fact that
there's no sugars,

42:37.689 --> 42:40.924
we're gonna end up
with less abv in this batch.

