42:46.898 --> 42:48.932
-It goes poof.
-Woah!

42:48.967 --> 42:50.233
That's sure good.

42:50.235 --> 42:52.435
Let's go ahead
and cap this up.

42:53.405 --> 42:55.004
Damn.

42:55.640 --> 42:58.174
You know after
it reaches about 170,

