There'll be liquor
out of here
any minute.

43:09.921 --> 43:11.955
It works quick, ain't it?

43:11.957 --> 43:13.256
Is it done here?

43:13.558 --> 43:14.591
You tell me.

43:14.593 --> 43:18.094
-Oh, yeah. Look, look, look.
-Liquor, puss.

43:18.096 --> 43:20.330
Glad we've dropped
old dodger in there.

43:21.800 --> 43:22.865
There we go!

43:22.867 --> 43:24.901
That's fine stream
right there.

43:24.903 --> 43:26.836
You know, everything's heated
up right now,

43:26.838 --> 43:28.871
starting to push
liquor through.

