Ultrasonic?
What the hell is that?

45:18.683 --> 45:21.751
[jaime] the first agave
I planted was here
in this area.

45:21.753 --> 45:26.856
This land belongs
to our family from more
than 70 years, maybe.

45:26.858 --> 45:29.892
My whole reason I'm here,
I wanna know
how do you make tequila.

45:29.894 --> 45:32.428
You know,
where does it come from?

45:32.430 --> 45:34.764
All the agave we have here
