Do you have to buy
it from somewhere?

46:10.034 --> 46:14.771
We, we take care
of the smaller agaves,
the baby agaves, the seeds.

46:14.773 --> 46:16.139
And we replant it.

46:16.141 --> 46:18.875
-You see those small,
baby agaves over there?
-I see it coming up.

46:18.877 --> 46:20.710
-Such a sprout.
