One by one by hand.
I contract guys.

46:43.434 --> 46:44.834
So, they're gonna plant it,

46:44.836 --> 46:48.571
and they're gonna watch
over it every year
until they harvest it

46:48.573 --> 46:50.606
and then they have to come
and chop it,

46:50.608 --> 46:52.575
<i>  and then take</i>
<i>  it to the distillery.</i>

46:52.577 --> 46:55.044
Remember when you have
a glass of tequila
in your hand,

46:55.046 --> 46:57.914
seven years ago,
that is a lot of people,

46:57.916 --> 47:00.249
-around here
planted the agave.
