than this, yes.

47:15.733 --> 47:17.733
You want to try
the best tequila

47:17.735 --> 47:21.704
-and you compare,
you got to try both areas.
-Mmm-hmm.

47:21.706 --> 47:24.073
He recommends that
I go to the highlands,

47:24.075 --> 47:25.441
which is a couple
of hours away,

47:25.443 --> 47:28.578
<i>  where the blue agave</i>
<i>  is grown in a different</i>
<i>  environment.</i>

47:28.580 --> 47:31.614
And it also gives a different
taste profile to the tequila.

47:31.616 --> 47:35.017
So, I'm gonna get the taste
of something else.

47:35.019 --> 47:37.620
So we finished
the field of agaves.

47:37.622 --> 47:38.554
Yeah.

47:38.556 --> 47:40.790
That was a good,
educational trip.

47:40.792 --> 47:43.426
It's very special for my
first time in mexico.

47:43.428 --> 47:45.928
<i>  Just meeting with jaime</i>
<i>  was a great honor.</i>

47:45.930 --> 47:47.997
It's time to go back.
